{"tid":130104,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【蟹出沒注意】70歲鄭少秋5月開騷：今次個市全部會升","createTime":"2017-02-22T06:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T03:35:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b9c8adadc934e1a0887f66360392ec80901a466","tid":130104,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170222/s00007/ea4e712db329671f4589ee162813d605.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170222%2Fs00007%2Fea4e712db329671f4589ee162813d605.jpg&h=513252d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n快將70歲的鄭少秋（秋官），將於5月28日及29日，假紅館舉行《鄭少秋半世紀大時代世界巡迴演唱會》﹐早前在多份報章出現一個神秘廣告，寫上「蟹出沒注意」，原來就是為慶祝秋官入行50年的宣傳策略。秋官說：「我就係想吸引我班蟹民，等佢哋知道我出現，再話畀佢哋聽，今次個市全部都會升，快啲入貨，賺多啲。」<br />\n<br />\n在《大時代》飾演「丁蟹」的秋官，成為股民的熊市指標，認為只要有秋官的演出，股市都會跌。今次演唱會在5月舉行，被投資者形容為「五窮六絕七翻身」的港股，加埋「丁蟹效應」，必引起股壇熱話，但秋官睇好兼唱好後市：「你哋以往都話，逢係我嘅演出，股票都會跌，但今次就唔同，係升，但你哋記得嚟捧我場，先會升㗎喎，知道嗎！」<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170222/s00007/1487739421720#sthash.rNFXQ95q.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170222%2Fs00007%2F1487739421720%23sthash.rNFXQ95q.dpuf&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=7e4d676b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170222%2Fs00007%2F1487739421720%23sthash.rNFXQ95q.dpuf&h=15e5a905\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170222/s00007/1487739421720#sthash.rNFXQ95q.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"e0fe91e02cbd5b211930062063a4a1b5c0e51e8d","tid":130104,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:47:04.000Z","msg":"丁蟹+五窮+十年一大跌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n準備all in熊證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5faeb0